Class DaqDeviceInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.DaqDeviceInfo

public class DaqDeviceInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to retrieve information that describe the DAQ device. To create an instance of this class, call the getInfo() method of the DaqDevice class.
